### Enrichment
GF lemon crinkle cookies use almond flour base for tender melt-in-mouth texture. Key technique: rub lemon zest into sugar to infuse flavor. Chill dough 2+ hours before rolling. Roll in powdered sugar for signature crinkle effect. Cream of tartar helps with texture. Popular versions from The Loopy Whisk, Snixy Kitchen use almond flour for naturally GF approach. Consider noting which flour blend works best (almond flour vs GF blend).

